<lb ed="X" n="0626c03"/><item id="itemX74p0626c0301">南無金剛手菩薩</item><item id="itemX74p0626c0308">南無華嚴首菩薩</item></list>
<lb ed="X" n="0626c04"/><p id="pX74p0626c0401" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">遶畢歸位復舉</note>。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0626c05"/><list><item id="itemX74p0626c0501">自皈依佛當願眾生紹隆佛種發無上心</item>
<lb ed="X" n="0626c06"/><item id="itemX74p0626c0601">自皈依法當願眾生深入經藏智慧如海</item>
<lb ed="X" n="0626c07"/><item id="itemX74p0626c0701">自皈依僧當願眾生統理大眾一切無礙</item>
<lb ed="X" n="0626c08"/><item id="itemX74p0626c0801">和南聖眾</item></list>
<lb ed="X" n="0626c09"/><p id="pX74p0626c0901" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">復稱南無本師釋迦牟尼佛。出壇入觀堂觀時。一心誦&CB00057;。香完自便</note>。</p></div1>
